snippet.description:
Amber Heard Wants Harry Potter Role Since Johnny Depp Is Gone | Celebrity Craze

Amber Heard Faces 10 Years In Prison For Lying In Court! | Celebrity Craze

While some celebrities prefer living a quiet life away from the public, others just have so many scandals following them. In this video, we are going to talk about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, who have been on each other’s throats ever since they split up.

Even though Amber Heard might be facing jail time for one mistake she made; she is still trying to make Johnny Depp suffer. Now she is trying to go after movie roles that have since dropped Johnny Depp. The Fantastic Beasts and Harry Potter roles being the most prominent.
